{"tid":327344,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"死啦！前排聆聽因為無帶電芯 入左特別室","createTime":"2017-07-18T16:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T04:53:23.000Z","uid":110080,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2727814c4b04977567ccdefe97f95305a32df6a","tid":327344,"uid":110080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:31:48.000Z","msg":"是咁的，前排我原本帶左兩粒金霸王電芯去應考架，係半路覺得唔放心，拎左出黎睇下，點知地下濕滑，天氣唔好，大風得滯，我果兩粒電芯跌左落水溝到執唔番。 <br />\n<br />\n係呢個時候，有個人從水溝入面上左黎，佢 =<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   ，我 =  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：你係咪搵緊一粒電芯啊？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：係啊.... <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：我呢度有粒銅霸王，係咪你架？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：唔係啊，係金霸王啊 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：我呢度有粒銀霸王，係咪你架？ <br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔係啊，係金霸王啊 <br />\n<br />\n佢見我唔開心，又入番落水搵多陣&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n過多陣，佢又上番黎，手上拎住支洗頭水 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：我呢度有支「霸王」，係咪你架？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：唔係啊，係金霸王啊 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：見你咁誠實，我送曬三樣俾你啦 <br />\n<br />\n最後我聆聽因為無帶電芯，要入特別室，唔知會唔會扣分，唉"},{"pid":"9e05968decc70785191d4ac188e184d66598d2ee","tid":327344,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:33:13.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221e2363a8a0f4ab23f4ca11fd4b4a93887ba5e9","tid":327344,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:33:45.000Z","msg":"幽"},{"pid":"719299bbb640dc2ea6144cb552ded29d94a8dcc6","tid":327344,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:34:30.000Z","msg":"嘻"},{"pid":"eae263141d91b2cd2d563d8ddd7d27928cf48147","tid":327344,"uid":74598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:35:10.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"e533ba502d3d83fefc00f3e2f3bbfb8b90a36aa8","tid":327344,"uid":16045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:36:04.000Z","msg":"哈.哈."},{"pid":"b116ac3f55e96e5b26f7a6e5fcf4158119b01822","tid":327344,"uid":1858,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:37:45.000Z","msg":"唔會嫁，因為d老師知你弱智先要入特別室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11b936fdbe55aa245c26784d696154f09f89cf9","tid":327344,"uid":110080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:38:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會嫁，因為d老師知你弱智先要入特別室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fcbcf49371d120bdc69ff5de488e7de1c8929b8","tid":327344,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T04:42:59.000Z","msg":"幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e651b8258a76bf39783da3ef858c09d1eb72884a","tid":327344,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T04:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39416bf06ae88359b99a89e86df2be2b9bd777af","tid":327344,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,